See you in a bit.

324
00:22:51,120 --> 00:22:52,395
<i>How does he do that?</i>

325
00:22:54,920 --> 00:22:57,958
Is it here? No, no, it's here.

326
00:22:58,400 --> 00:23:00,278
All right, folks.

327
00:23:00,480 --> 00:23:01,550
I always get this wrong.

328
